observations.recommendation:
We recommended that the Municipal Mayor instruct the Municipal Accountant to:
reconcile the FS balance with the supporting schedules relating to Due to GSIS account;
identify the transactions that caused the discrepancy to reconcile with the balance obtained by the Audit Team from the confirmation with the GSIS;
cause the immediate remittance of any unremitted contributions and loan amortization payments to avoid incurrence of penalties and surcharges; and
come up with appropriate measures to ensure that monthly withheld premium contributions and loan amortization payments are remitted promptly and accurately.

We recommended and the BAC, through the BAC Secretariat, agreed to undertake the following:
Comply with GPPB Circular No. 02-2020 on the submission of the PMR and APCPI Results to the GPPB using the above provided email addresses;
Inquire with the GPPB on the reason of non-posting of the submitted CYs 2023 and 2024 APPs, which was duly acknowledged by them, to be guided and ensure the posting of the next reports that will be submitted by the agency;
Post the duly approved PMR in the agency’s website; and
Coordinate with the personnel assigned in the maintenance of the agency’s website to resolve the issue on the non-posting of APPs.

