observations.recommendation:
We recommend that the Municipal Accountant require the submission of the documents to support the entry debiting the account Due to NGAs as follow
1. Financial /status reports of the Project;
2. Certificate of Acceptance if the project has been fully completed;
3. Authorization of the claimant for labor services by persons other than the concerned laborers;
4. Approved request for the diversion of the original project proposal to the direct implementation of the cassava production by the Cooperative; and
5. Review correctness of the paid payrolls presented to support claim for labor services.
Reverse the entry made taking up the liquidation of P 1,500,000.00 if the above-mentioned documents could not be submitted.
